Notice: Please use with wooden shovel! Steel shovel/utensil/scrubber will hurt the non-stick coating; Dishwasher is not suggested, it may hurt the handle

Product feature:
- Healthy and durable
  High quality ILAG Swiss Granistone passed American FDA inspection SGS certification PFOA FREE
- Strengthen protection 5-layer process
  Imported 5-layer non-stick coating, wear resistant up to 50,000 times
- Excellent non-stick performance
- Less oil needed, healthy cooking
- Double spouts design

Mainteinance:
1. First confirm the product's quality when you receive it
2. Then use normal dishwashing liquid&soap water and sponge to wash it twice or three times with warm water
3. Wipe off water stains or put 1-2 spoon of cookingg oil on the surface if you like
4. Set it aside before the next use
5. Make sure the lids only be closed after wiping off water stains or after air-drying
6. It is prohibited to boil that empty or dry
